The Odyssey - In Theaters 07.17.26

Christopher Nolan‚Äôs next film, The Odyssey, is a mythic action epic shot across the world using brand new IMAX¬Æ film technology. The film brings Homer‚Äôs foundational saga to IMAX¬Æ film screens for the first time and opens in theaters everywhere on July 17, 2026. 

The Odyssey stars Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, Robert Pattinson and Lupita Nyong‚Äôo, with Zendaya and Charlize Theron.

The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

snippet.title: YABI - BOOMERANG ( OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO )
snippet.description:
Artist/Performer: YABI THE G.O.A.T
Recorded at: Kadak Nepali
Prod. By: Rick Anthony
Mixed & Mastered by: Ruthlexx
Mixtape: Bommerang
Directed: Samirvision

Boomerang is a raw and emotional record that comes back harder every time just like the feelings it carries.This track dives into love, pain, and the moments you can‚Äôt escape no matter how far you run.Recorded at Kadak Nepali and mixed & mastered by Ruthlexx, Boomerang brings heavy energy with a polished sound.
This song is a part of my mixtape Boomerang, a project that reflects real stories, real emotions, and real experiences.Turn the volume up, feel the bounce, and let it hit you back.This is Boomerang.

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - ‚ÄúThor odinson Will Return‚Äù Trailer | Chris Hemsworth (Concept Version)
snippet.description:
‚Äî Attention Viewers ‚ö†Ô∏è
‚Äî This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
‚Äî Avengers: Doomsday - Thor odinson Will Return

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story reframes the coming conflict through the weight of legacy and responsibility rather than spectacle, centering on a world where familiar heroes are no longer driven by glory but by what they stand to lose. As the multiversal order begins to fracture under an unseen but deliberate hand, the Avengers are forced to confront a threat that challenges not only their strength, but their purpose. Thor‚Äôs journey anchors the narrative, revealing a god who has fought for realms and crowns now facing a far more human fear: the need to protect a future embodied in a single child. Doctor Doom emerges not as a force of chaos, but as a calculated architect convinced the multiverse itself must be corrected, placing him on a collision course with heroes who now fight not as warriors, but as guardians. The trailer positions Doomsday as a reckoning, where duty, parenthood, and sacrifice redefine what it truly means to be an Avenger when the fate of existence demands more than victory‚Äîit demands return.

‚Äî  Subscribe to Teaser Universe üé¨
‚Äî  For inquiries: teaseruniverse@gmail.com üì©

#doomsday #thor #avengers

The fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,

snippet.title: Arjun Katuwal - Teri Meri Kahani (Official Music Video) Nimesh Shrestha || Barsha kshetri || Vague
snippet.description:
This song is a humble tribute to the beautiful but heartbreaking love story of Bibek Pangeni and Srijana Subedi, a couple who showed the world what true love, courage, and devotion really look like.
Their journey reminded us that love is not just about the smiles we share, but also the battles we fight together, hand in hand.
It is our way of honoring a love that touched millions and continues to inspire people everywhere.

To Bibek, your strength and smile will never be forgotten.
To Srijana, your love and dedication remain a timeless example of what it means to stand by someone with your whole heart.
And to everyone watching, may their story remind you to cherish the people you love a little more today.

Audio credits :
Music & Production: Arjun Katuwal
Asst Music producer: Bibas Music (FREQ Temple)
Lyrics: Ritik Koul (Vague)
Mix & Master : Pukhraj Sonkar(inhouse studio)
Violins : Krishna Raj
Strings Orchestrated : Rakesh Venkatapuram
Flute : Swarnim Maharjan

snippet.description:
#tukimusic  #pokhara #nephop 
TUKI MUSIC - Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)


"Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)" is a revolutionary song that captures the emotional turmoil relating to death of ‚ÄúGen Z ‚Äú protesters in Nepal. On 9 September 2025, protesters angered by government repression and corruption stormed the Nepalese Federal Parliament Building in Kathmandu. The protest escalated when the police killed 19 protesters including a 12-year-old child on 8 September 2025. Through this evocative lyrics and soulful melody, the song portrays frustration of Nepalese Youth towards corruption and political insanity.

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single - Inaam, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Sanju Rathod presents 'Shaky' a Marathi track like no other!

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. Sanju Rathod and Isha Malviya bring effortless swag, catchy hooks, and vibrant energy in this fun, feel-good love track. A bold, danceable vibe that pushes Marathi music into exciting new territory.

snippet.title: NEW CONTROL REWORK IN BLOX FRUITS!
snippet.description:
Today I reacted to the new control rework! Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens. 

FOLTYN MERCH: https://foltyn.shop/

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/1177555...

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/foltynn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Aankhama Chasma Chyattai - Roj Moktan | Jamuna Yonjan | Amir Dong | Bipashna | Nisha | Kuisang
snippet.description:
A brand-new fusion of Selo and Nadhing Selo arrives with the energetic creation ‚ÄúAankhama Chasma Chyattai.‚Äù This special version carries emotion, rhythm, and nostalgia as Roj Moktan and Jamuna Yonjan lend their voices together after 20 long years, creating a powerful moment of musical reunion.

The lyrics, written by Jivan Bomjan Tamang and Roj Moktan, pair seamlessly with the music composed by Roj Moktan, giving the song a modern heartbeat while preserving its cultural depth.

The music video features dynamic performances by Amir Dong, Bipashna Tamang, Nisha Lama, and Kuisang Rumba, each adding expressive storytelling that enhances the flow and feeling of the song.

Guided by the direction of Amir Dong, the visuals carry a strong sense of culture, emotion, and cinematic style, resulting in a compelling and memorable presentation.

The lyrics, written by Jivan Bomjan Tamang and Roj Moktan, pair seamlessly with the music composed by Roj Moktan, giving the song a modern heartbeat while preserving its cultural depth.
